Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊... 阿哈... 阿呵...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bo... BoBi~

Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說些什麼...
